锁码,电话拨号和关机界面采用新设计以及全新的滑动来解锁动画。此外,电话、FaceTime和信息应用的图标颜色也进行了更新。</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.7;&quot;><a class=&quot;highslide-image&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 136, 204); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.guoshe.net/wp-content/plugins/auto-highslide/highslide/graphics/zoomin.cur), pointer;&quot; href=&quot;http://guoshe.qiniudn.com/wp-content/uploads/ta-thumbnails-cache/TAdownload/2014/2/15108-1.jpg&quot;><img alt=&quot;http://www.guoshe.net/wp-content/uploads/ta-thumbnails-cache/TAdownload/2014/2/15108-1.jpgg&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; display: inline;&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/05/1391570822799.jpg&quot; /></a></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.7;&quot;>iOS 7.1 beta 5的新功能包括:</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.7;&quot;>-iOS 7.1 beta 5中英语(澳大利亚)、英语(英国)、日语和中文(普通话)可以支持选择声音性别了</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.7;&quot;>-<a target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 136, 204);&quot;>键盘</a>Shift和Caps按键外观改善,傻傻分不清的问题解决了!</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.7;&quot;><a class=&quot;highslide-image&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 136, 204); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.guoshe.net/wp-content/plugins/auto-hi