16266417	情何以堪的QQ群群主!	<p style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;有这么一个群体,他们无时不刻都在中枪,而且枪枪都很经典!对,我说的就是QQ群的群主!</p><p style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>  QQ群,伴随着QQ的成长一路走来,是规模和影响力不容小视。谁的QQ没有加入一个QQ群,谁没有在QQ群里冒过泡!但也正如你知道的,在群里,不管你是潜水或是在线,你总会在QQ群看到这么一个现象,冷不丁跳出一个消息,比如说:&ldquo;群主怀孕了,不知道是谁干的?&rdquo;、&ldquo;群主被大灰狼带走之后,就再也没有回来了&rdquo;。这让群主看到了情何以堪啊。</p><p style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>  </p><center style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;><a style=&quot;color: rgb(58, 96, 167); font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.sootoo.com/slide/341680_1.shtml&quot;><img style=&quot;padding: 3px; border: currentColor; max-width: 600px; background-image: none;&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/16/1392554595120.jpg&quot; width=&quot;378&quot; height=&quot;212&quot; /></a></center><p style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>  </p><center style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;><a style=&quot;color: rgb(58, 96, 167); font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.sootoo.com/slide/341680_2.shtml&quot;><img style=&quot;padding: 3px; border: currentColor; max-width: 600px; background-image: none;&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/16/1392554595196.jpg&quot; width=&quot;388&quot; height=&quot;242&quot; /></a></center><p style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>  群主,百度百科给出的解释:群的创建者拥有群内的最高权限,掌管着群内生杀予夺的权力,因此被称为&ldquo;群主&rdquo;。</p><p style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>  建群是为了交流,但群里很多人都不是很熟,但有时又想活跃一下气氛,但是找不到话题,可怜的群主,这时就成了靶子,比如说:&ldquo;儿啊,我们来找你父亲了,听说他当上群主了!&rdquo;、&ldquo;听说群主在我们那里搞按摩,给抓了。&rdquo;&ldquo;难怪,今天都没有听到他在群里说话!&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;群主,就这样无声无息的中枪了。</p><p style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>  </p><center style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;><a style=&quot;color: rgb(58, 96, 167); font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.sootoo.com/slide/341680_3.shtml&quot;><img style=&quot;padding: 3px; border: currentColor; max-width: 600px; background-image: none;&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/16/1392554595295.jpg&quot; width=&quot;349&quot; height=&quot;286&quot; /></a></center><center style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>&nbsp;</center><center style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;><a style=&quot;color: rgb(58, 96, 167); font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.sootoo.com/slide/341680_4.shtml&quot;><img style=&quot;padding: 3px; border: currentColor; max-width: 600px; background-image: none;&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/16/1392554595420.jpg&quot; width=&quot;353&quot; height=&quot;345&quot; /></a></center><p style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>  而逢年过节,群主被调侃的几率那是打开哪个群,哪个群都是的要求群主发礼品的,比如说中秋节要到了,最常见的是:&ldquo;群主,中秋节又快到了!又没有月饼发?(很大声的说)你对得住我们吗?你自己看着办吧!&rdquo;</p><p style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>  </p><center style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;><a style=&quot;color: rgb(58, 96, 167); font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.sootoo.com/slide/341680_5.shtml&quot;><img style=&quot;padding: 3px; border: currentColor; max-width: 600px; background-image: none;&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/16/1392554595544.jpg&quot; width=&quot;245&quot; height=&quot;171&quot; /></a></center><p style=&quot;font: 14px/23px SimSun, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word