font:<br/>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>个数据中心,已建成的</span><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>12</span><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;<br/>mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br/>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>个数据中心以及</span><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>SoftLayer</span><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:<br/>Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br/>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>的</span><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>13</span><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;<br/>mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br/>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>个数据中心。新建的数据中心将分布在中国、华盛顿特区、香港、伦敦、日本、印度、加拿大、墨西哥和达拉斯。根据这项最新的发布,</span><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>IBM</span><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;<br/>mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br/>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>公司计划在所有主要地区和金融中心实现数据中心覆盖,并计划在</span><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>2015</span><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;<br/>mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br/>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>年向中东和非洲扩张。</span></p><p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>&nbsp;</span></p><p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;<br/>mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br/>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>请注意,这是一个非常庞大的计划,甚至比当年摩托罗拉的铱星计划有过之而无不及,加上在</span><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>2013</span><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;<br/>mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br/>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>年花费</span><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>20</span><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;<br/>mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br/>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>亿美元收购的</span><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>SoftLayer</span><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:<br/>Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br/>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>,</span><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>IBM</span><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;<br/>mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br/>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>可以说将赌注都押在了云计算上。</span></p><p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>&nbsp;</span></p><p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>IBM</span><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;<br/>mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:<br/>宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;<br/>mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>在云计算上并不乐观,他面临着亚马逊、微软等对手的强大冲击,再不聚焦,或许输掉的是未来。</span></p><p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>&nbsp;</span></p><p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;<br/>mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br/>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>值得注意的是,南冥一鲨猜测,</span><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>IBM</span><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;<br/>mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br/>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>卖服务器业务给联想,很有可能不是一场简单的交易,两家公司很有可能联手拓展云计算市场。事实上,在中国,</span><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>IBM</span><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;<br/>mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br/>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>单单靠自己力量根本玩不转,因为要推云计算,不是简单的卖机器或服务那么简单,随便搜搜,</span><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>IBM</span><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;<br/>mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br/>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>在各地建设所谓的云谷,还有所谓的智慧城市,已经深入到国家的基础设施。</span></p><p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>&nbsp;</span></p><p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>IBM</span><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;<br/>mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:<br/>宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;<br/>mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>是否会借服务器业务的交易,加深与联想的关系,曲线拓展中国的云计算市场,也未可知,让我们拭目以待吧。</span></p><p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>&nbsp;</span></p><p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;><b><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;<br/>mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:<br/>Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;>南冥一鲨:互联网行业资深从业者,希望以自己的冷静观察,激浊扬清。欢迎订阅我的微信公众号:</span><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;>southsharker</span></b><b><span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-t