tom: 0pt&quot; class=&quot;p0&quot;><span style=&quot;font-family: '宋体'; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'&quot;>拿下IBM服务器业务是媒体多年关注的焦点,虽然如今仅是IBM的部分业务,但这一步终于联想还是迈出了一步。</span><span style=&quot;font-family: '宋体'; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'&quot;><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=&quot;line-height: 125%; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; class=&quot;p0&quot;><span style=&quot;font-family: '宋体'; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'&quot;>那么对于服务器市场来说,联想此次收购对谁威胁最大?会砸了谁的饭碗,这是大家比较关注的话题。</span><span style=&quot;font-family: '宋体'; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'&quot;><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=&quot;line-height: 125%; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; class=&quot;p0&quot;><span style=&quot;font-style: normal; font-family: '宋体'; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-shading: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;>Gartner发布</span><span style=&quot;font-style: normal; font-family: '宋体'; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-shading: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;>的</span><span style=&quot;font-style: normal; font-family: '宋体'; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-shading: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;>第</span><span style=&quot;font-style: normal; font-family: '宋体'; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-shading: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;>二</span><span style=&quot;font-style: normal; font-family: '宋体'; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-shading: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;>季度服务器</span><span style=&quot;font-style: normal; font-family: '宋体'; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rg